Package: echor
Type: Package
Title: Access EPA ECHO Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Michael Schramm
Maintainer: Michael Schramm <michael.schramm@ag.tamu.edu>
Description: An R interface to EPA ECHO API. ECHO provides information
    about EPA permitted facilities, discharges, and other reporting info 
    associated with permitted entities. Data are obtained from 
    <https://echo.epa.gov/>. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
